{"word":"διακινέω","slug":"διακινέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διακινέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to move thoroughly</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be put in motion</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to throw into disorder, confound</i>, <el>τὰ πεπραγμένα</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sift thoroughly, scrutinise</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}